analysis: The agent included an unsupported parameter "investmentHorizon" in its SIP_TSI function call, causing the evaluator to reject it as not matching the expected schema. Only the required parameters should have been provided.

The agent omitted the required "contactMethod" parameter ("Email") in the SNE_MS function call, resulting in a mismatch with the expected function signature and causing the evaluator to reject the output.
The agent incorrectly added an unsupported parameter "recipeComplexity": "Easy" to the NRC_LCR function call, which did not match the tool's defined parameters, resulting in a mismatch failure.
The agent omitted the required "outputDetail": "Summary" parameter in the TAT_MI function call, resulting in a mismatch with the expected function call structure.

The agent called the correct function (EL_NE) with the right location but omitted the required "eventType" parameter ("Concert"), resulting in an incomplete function call that did not match the expected input structure.

The agent called the correct function (GF_UIFG) with the correct interest parameter but omitted the required "ratingThreshold": "good" parameter, failing to filter recommendations by rating as specified in the user request.

The agent selected the incorrect function (TravelRoutePlanner_generateScenicRoute_1) instead of the required TRP_SR function, despite both having the same purpose. It failed to match the expected tool call by name, resulting in no matching function call.
The agent failed to normalize the timezone parameter, passing "Eastern Standard Time" instead of the required abbreviation "EST," resulting in a parameter mismatch for the AAA_AT function call.

The agent incorrectly used a numeric rating ("9.0") instead of the required categorical value ("high") for the "rating" parameter in the GD_NGBI function, resulting in a parameter mismatch and no valid function call match.
